  "caption": [
    {
      "start_time": "00:00:00.000",
      "end_time": "00:00:00.400",
      "text": "Today"
    },
    {
      "start_time": "00:00:00.401",
      "end_time": "00:00:03.480",
      "text": "I'm showing you the redesign of a hero section I did some time ago,"
    },
    {
      "start_time": "00:00:03.600",
      "end_time": "00:00:05.600",
      "text": "the one from trigify.io"
    },
    {
      "start_time": "00:00:05.601",
      "end_time": "00:00:07.320",
      "text": "As you can see, nothing's disastrous."
    },
    {
      "start_time": "00:00:07.640",
      "end_time": "00:00:09.880",
      "text": "Overall, there's a good hierarchy of social proof"
    },
    {
      "start_time": "00:00:10.280",
      "end_time": "00:00:11.480",
      "text": "and the call to action is present."
    },
    {
      "start_time": "00:00:11.520",
      "end_time": "00:00:13.680",
      "text": "But it doesn't yet have a clear brand vibe"
    },
    {
      "start_time": "00:00:13.760",
      "end_time": "00:00:15.520",
      "text": "and the hero section is very descriptive,"
    },
    {
      "start_time": "00:00:15.800",
      "end_time": "00:00:16.680",
      "text": "Very tool-focused."
    },
    {
      "start_time": "00:00:16.719",
      "end_time": "00:00:19.760",
      "text": "So the goal was to put more focus on the main message"
    },
    {
      "start_time": "00:00:20.160",
      "end_time": "00:00:21.320",
      "text": "and the expected action."
    },
    {
      "start_time": "00:00:21.360",
      "end_time": "00:00:23.800",
      "text": "For that, I reworked a more emotional promise,"
    },
    {
      "start_time": "00:00:24.000",
      "end_time": "00:00:25.120",
      "text": "more about what's missing,"
    },
    {
      "start_time": "00:00:25.280",
      "end_time": "00:00:27.720",
      "text": "plus a visual style that highlights this"
    },
    {
      "start_time": "00:00:27.880",
      "end_time": "00:00:29.200",
      "text": "message and the desired action."
    },
    {
      "start_time": "00:00:29.280",
      "end_time": "00:00:31.640",
      "text": "Now we're not just talking about what the product does"
    },
    {
      "start_time": "00:00:31.760",
      "end_time": "00:00:34.320",
      "text": "but what users don't want to miss anymore. Visually,"
    },
    {
      "start_time": "00:00:34.400",
      "end_time": "00:00:36.080",
      "text": "the eye isn't guided in the same way."
    },
    {
      "start_time": "00:00:36.120",
      "end_time": "00:00:38.560",
      "text": "Here, the product hasn't changed but the perception has."
    },
    {
      "start_time": "00:00:38.561",
      "end_time": "00:00:41.840",
      "text": "And of course, here's the responsive version because let me remind you"
    },
    {
      "start_time": "00:00:41.960",
      "end_time": "00:00:45.040",
      "text": "at least 70% of your visitors use mobile."
    },
    {
      "start_time": "00:00:45.160",
      "end_time": "00:00:46.560",
      "text": "Feel free to tell me what you think"
    },
    {
      "start_time": "00:00:46.561",
      "end_time": "00:00:48.560",
      "text": "and if you want me to redesign your hero section,"
    },
    {
      "start_time": "00:00:49.000",
      "end_time": "00:00:49.960",
      "text": "drop the link in the comments."
    }
  ]
}